                  "pageId": 1090048,
                  "revisionId": 2783786,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The taunt overrides other targeting modifiers such as Radiation status and Nyx 's Chaos . Friendly fire is not disabled, so confused enemies can still incidentally damage, and be damaged by, their former allies."
                }
